Package: DTD
Title: Digital Tissue Deconvolution
Version: 0.9
Authors@R: person("Marian", "Sch<U+00F6>n", email = "marian.schoen@klinik.uni-regensburg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Digital Tissue Deconvolution (DTD) estimates the cellular composition c of reference profiles X in a tissue sample y. Here we provide functions and routines to a loss-function learning DTD approach published by Goertler et al 2018. 
